'''Ingegärd Margareta Töpel''' (13 May 1906 – 11 July 1988) was a [[Sweden|Swedish]] diver. She competed in the 10 m platform event at the [[1928 Summer Olympics]], alongside her elder sister [[Hjördis Töpel|Hjördis]].<ref name=SR>{{cite web|title=Ingegärd Töpel |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/to/ingegard-topel-1.html |website=Sports Reference |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304030022/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/to/ingegard-topel-1.html |archivedate=4 March 2016 |df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref name=sok>[http://sok.se/idrottare/idrottare/i/ingegard-topel.html Ingegärd Töpel]. Swedish Olympic Committee</ref>
