{{distinguish|Susan Werner}} {{one source|date=January 2013}} {{Infobox person | name = Susana Werner | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1977|7|20}} | birth_place = [[Rio de Janeiro]], Brazil | residence = [[Lisbon]], [[Portugal]] | occupation = Actress and model | spouse = [[Júlio César (football goalkeeper, born 1979)|Júlio César]] (m. 2002) | children = 2 }}
'''Susana Werner''' (born July 20, 1977) is a Brazilian model and actress.
==Personal life== From 1997 to 1999, Susana Werner had a relationship with Brazilian footballer [[Ronaldo Nazario|Ronaldo]]. Later, she married the Brazilian goalkeeper [[Júlio César Soares Espíndola|Júlio César]]. The couple has two children, Cauet (born in 2002) and Giulia (born in 2005).<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lancenet.com.br/noticias/09-01-29/477266.stm?susana-werner-amor-em-milao |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2009-02-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090304002515/http://lancenet.com.br/noticias/09-01-29/477266.stm?susana-werner-amor-em-milao |archivedate=2009-03-04 |df= }} </ref>
In June 2013, Werner was robbed at gunpoint after her car was stopped as she drove through [[Fortaleza]] late at night.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/06/20/soccer-confederations-crime-idUKL3N0EW3U320130620 |title=Soccer-Brazil goalkeeper's wife robbed at gunpoint in Fortaleza |first=Brian |last=Homewood |agency=Reuters |date=20 June 2013 |accessdate=25 May 2014}}</ref>
